---
title: Creamy Pork & Green Bean Fettuccine with Cheesy Garlic Bread & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: This may be our fanciest pasta night yet! Luxurious herby seasoning takes this creamy pork fettuccine from simply amazing to totally outrageous, adding a new depth of flavour to an already flavour-packed dish. Cheesy garlic bread and a fresh salad are the perfect partners in crime.
